<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>This type represents a <db:link xlink:href="qcamerapermission.xml">QCameraPermission</db:link>, and can be used to check the status of and request access to the user's camera.</db:para>
<db:para>See <db:link xlink:href="qcamerapermission.xml">QCameraPermission</db:link> for documentation of the individual properties and detailed usage requirements.</db:para>
